Transformation QA Report
========================

Compares previous and current versions of:
  1. Programme Demand (Demand.xlsx)
  2. Load / Capability (LoadCap.xlsx)
  3. SharpCloud Skills Data (SCSkillsData.xlsx)

It also reconciles Programme Demand against LoadCap by Year Quarter + HoC.

Run normally for file-picker dialogs:
    python transformation_qa_report.py

Required packages:
    pip install pandas openpyxl numpy

Optional command-line use is supported. Run:
    python transformation_qa_report.py --help
"""

